# Handwritten Digit Recognition (OCR) using CNN

This project implements an Optical Character Recognition (OCR) system to recognize handwritten digits (0-9) using a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN). The model is trained on the MNIST dataset, a large dataset of handwritten digits, and can be used to predict the digits in new images.

